summary:
This is an interesting logic game where you should paint cells on a paper with a pencil to get to the exit.   

Rules of this conundrum game are pretty simple:   
1) pencil can go across cells which do not have the same color as the pencil;   
2) you can change color of the pencil, to do that you should put it on a cell with a little pencil icon;   
3) no turns are allowed within a single move - pencil can go only along a line.   

Have fun solving interesting puzzles and train your brain!
